name: Able Pasadena Movers
overview: Able Pasadena Movers is a company serving the relocating needs of people living in Pasadena at affordable rates. We know that moving from one place to another is a great task. Able Pasadena Movers will take care of all of your moving tasks. packing up a whole house, throwing away items and lifting the heavy boxes and other things can cause a headache. Unlike most other Movers in Pasadena, we are here to help you and make your relocation a memorable and comfortable experience.
